==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Creel
<hw>Creel</hw> <pr>(kr⟦emac⟧l)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gael.
<ets>craidhleag</ets> basket, creel.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>An osier basket, such as anglers use.</def>
<rj><au>Sir W. Scott.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Spinning)</fld> <def>A bar or set of bars with
skewers for holding paying-off bobbins, as in the roving machine,
throstle, and mule.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Creep</ent>⟦br⟧
